description: Transform your home gym experience with the Marcy Home Gym Workout Station, a versatile and durable all-in-one exercise machine designed to target your entire body. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned fitness enthusiast, this complete workout system provides everything you need for effective full-body training in the comfort of your own home. Engineered with a sturdy frame and high-quality materials, this home gym system ensures stability and durability, even during the most intense workouts. The inclusion of multiple exercise functions offers endless possibilities for training. With its compact design and adjustable components, it’s easy to customize your workout routine and maximize the efficiency of your space. The Marcy Home Gym Workout Station is not just about versatility, it’s built for performance. The leg developer delivers a powerful lower body workout, while the lat pulldown offers safe and controlled weightlifting. You can easily switch between exercises with the multi-cable system, allowing for seamless transitions between strength and endurance training. Designed with user convenience in mind, this machine is easy to use and provides smooth transitions throughout every exercise. Perfect for full-body workouts, the Marcy Home Gym Workout Station is a great investment for anyone looking to elevate their fitness journey at home.

title: Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Crunch Bench (BFAB20R), Lower & Upper Abdominal Muscles Workout Machine For Home Gym, Red/Black
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Benches › Adjustable Benches
description: Product DescriptionPerform a variety of ab exercises easily, effectively, and safely with the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20). The adjustable, ergonomic AB crunch bench seat can be adjusted into 3 different positions to accommodate a wide range of heights and motion. The AB workout bench seat is angled at 45-degrees and reclines to 2 different 5-degree angles for a wide range of motion. This abdominal bench with adjustable length, textured grip handles, standard weight post, and 2-position footrests make it is comfortable and easy to perform exercises such as ab crunches and knee raises. When assembled the Body-Solid Best Fitness Semi Recumbent AB Bench (BFAB20) measures 64 by 11 by 46 inches (L x W x H). The frame is backed by the Best Fitness 3-year Warranty and the parts are backed by a 1 year warranty.Amazon.comMake any time crunch time with the Best Fitness BFAB20 semi-recumbent ab crunch. Unlike some other ab machines--which require the agility of an acrobat to be thoroughly effective--the BFAB20 puts you in a comfortable seated position without sacrificing your workout efficiency. The ergonomically designed machine is built to help you tighten up your midsection, strengthen your back, and improve your core stability, with your choice of toning your lower abs with knees raises or your upper abs with abdominal crunches. To perform ab crunches, simply use the upholstered upper back support, textured grip handles, and standard weight post. Performing knee raises is just as easy thanks to the adjustable-length, two-position footrests. Add in a three-position upholstered seat--which starts at 45 degrees but offers two additional 5-degree reclining positions--and you have everything you need to design an effective ab regimen in the comfort of your own home.  The BFAB20 is an essential workout accessory because your core is where all your body movements originate. Your abdominal muscles support and protect your internal organs and aid in breathing, especially when you exhale. The abs also team up with your back muscles to control trunk motions, such as twisting and bending. The BFAB20 takes the next step by also strengthening and toning the front of the thighs and increasing hip flexibility. The end results include a flatter stomach, better defined abs, well-developed obliques, a more upright posture, and greater support for your spine. Other features include a 1.75-inch upholstered seat, a durable powder-coated finish, and safety pins and bolts that allow for easy disassembly or permanent setup. The BFAB20 measures 22 by 46 by 64 inches (W x H x D) and carries a three-year warranty.

features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

Product Description

After continuous improvement and upgrading, Chest fly machine 2.0 (Black) is here! Pick it and get your the first time experience that you can really feel your pec or rear delts kicking in and fatigue! 
What is the Sweet Spot of this Isolated Pec Fly Machine? 
Its increased stability provides more focus and juice to the targeted muscles because stabilizing muscles are not used. Due to your path of motion is fixed. Essentially, you can hone in on the muscle for added volume and activation. 
How this Machine Helps You to Build a Nice-Shaping Rear Delts? 
It isolates the rear delts and muscles of the upper back without using stabilizing muscles of the lower body. You also use the pad to rest your chest against for leverage, which allows you to reverse fly with a greater load. 
Pec and Rear Delt machine vs Function trainer! Why do you shoulder-pick this for a Chest or Rear Delt Workout? 
It is a plate-load and fixed machine movement with no deviation so you can hit the targeted your aim muscle group for better hypertrophy benefits. 
Pec and Rear Delt Machine vs. Dumbbell! Why you Should Pick this Machine for Chest or Rear Delt Workout? 
If you are a beginner, getting dumbbells up in a position to perform butterflies is pretty hard and you will not feel your pec or rear delts kicking in and fatigue. But this fixed path machine will perfectly solve this issue. 
Can You Adjust the Height of This Chest Machine? I’m 5.6ft, I am not Sure if This Fits? 
[All Height Friendly] Yeah,i'm 6.2ft and it works fine to me. This one comes with adjustable seats, allowing you to set the height to suit your exercise requirements and body size.

description: Product DescriptionAchieve total body conditioning with the free motion Powerline by Body-Solid Cable Crossover Machine. An extra-wide and tall mainframe offers easy access to a virtually endless array of high and low pulley exercises, letting you exercise almost every major muscle group in your body. The fully functional professional carriage system utilizes four high resin pulleys on each side with patented nylon bushing technology and eight sealed ball bearings for smooth, continuous movement during your cable workout. The top and bottom pulleys swivel smoothly with more than 180-degrees of motion for frictionless training in all directions. This cable cross machine accepts both Olympic and standard plates (each sold separately) and comes with two cable handles and one ankle strap. When assembled, the Powerline Cable Crossover Machine measures 112 by 39 by 82 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 133 pounds. It is backed by the Powerline 10-Year In-Home , which covers the frame for 10 years and all other parts for one year. Add the Lat Pull-Up/Chin-Up Station (GCA2) to add even more versatility (sold separately).Amazon.comThe Cable Crossover Machine from Powerline offers smooth and friction-free 180-degree motion that allows you to exercise virtually every major muscle group in your body. The system features a wide and tall mainframe with a sturdy build, that provides access to a variety of high and low pulley exercises. The professional carriage system utilizes patented nylon bushing technology and eight sealed ball bearing with large-diameter high resin pulleys to guarantee smooth operation. Can the ShredForce be used for leg workouts too? 
No - the ShredForce is specifically made to help you train your upper body, so it won't be safe to use as a leg trainer. 
When storing my ShredForce, should it be open or closed? 
The best way to store it is to lower the resistance level and close the arm exerciser. This way your hydraulics will stay in outstanding condition for much longer. 
Do the hydraulics on the exerciser leak oil during training? 
Absolutely not. The premium hydraulics built into the ShredForce are durable and made to feel absolutely outstanding during workouts - no leaks, no other issues. 
Who can benefit from the ShredForce? 
The compact form combined with a wide resistance range makes the ShredForce a great option for traveling athletes, people just getting back into training, folks who live in smaller spaces, and anyone who needs an extra boost of upper body strength. 
Will the ShredForce replace my dumbbells? 
While most people will be perfectly satisfied with the upper body workouts they can perform with the Shredforce, it isn't made to be a direct replacement for dumbbells, but rather a complement that covers the needs your dumbbells don't.

Why do we say that our machine is also suitable for beginners? 
V2 incline press machine can be suitable for beginners as it provides a guided movement and allows for easy adjustments to the weight and angle. 
Can the incline chest press machine help strengthen other muscles besides the chest? 
Certainly, the incline press machine primarily works the chest muscles (pectoralis major and minor), as well as the triceps and shoulders. It can also engage the core muscles as you stabilize your body during the exercise. 
Why should I consider using this incline bench press machine? 
Specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts, and with other 6 backrest positions to choose, our machine helps to build your chest sculpture faster. 
Why choose this machine with vertical grip options? 
Verticval grips can offer better ergonomic support, reducing strain on wrist, elbow and shoulder. With vertical grips, you can also allow for targeting upper chest more precisely, enhancing the overall effectiveness of your fitness routine.

items.name: Can the incline chest press machine help strengthen other muscles besides the chest?
items.text: Certainly, the incline press machine primarily works the chest muscles (pectoralis major and minor), as well as the triceps and shoulders. It can also engage the core muscles as you stabilize your body during the exercise.

items.name: Why should I consider using this incline bench press machine?
items.text: Specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts, and with other 6 backrest positions to choose, our machine helps to build your chest sculpture faster.

items.name: Why choose this machine with vertical grip options?
items.text: Verticval grips can offer better ergonomic support, reducing strain on wrist, elbow and shoulder. With vertical grips, you can also allow for targeting upper chest more precisely, enhancing the overall effectiveness of your fitness routine.

description: Experience intense lifting workouts in home or professional gyms with the Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Incline Press (LVIP). A converging press arm and independent, unilateral arm action deliver balanced muscle development for the upper body. Ergonomic hand grips offer different positional options, with gas-assisted start positions to get your lift started right. The press arms are adjustable to fit users of all sizes. With a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge steel mainframe and durable double-stitched upholstery, this leverage incline machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. Sealed bearing pivot points provide smooth, friction-free movement through every intense workout. Weight plate holders are built into the machine for easy storage (plates sold separately). When assembled, the Body-Solid ProClubLine Leverage Incline Press measures 71 by 53 by 41 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 167 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.

Full Range Adjustable: Rotary flywheel mechanism and pop pin design allow for easy adjustment. 27 selectable holes that enable you to achieve over 180 degrees of adjustment. It allows for complete control over your starting position.

Sculpt Core Muscles: The core acts as the center of your body and helps you utilize every other part of your body to maximum efficiency. Building strong abs can mean reduced back pain, higher quality posture, functional strength, increase in sports performance and better all-around balance. Ab machines can help fill the gap between bodyweight core training and a core hardened by progressive overload.

title: Valor Fitness Seated Row Machine - Plate Loaded- Converging Arms- Multi-Grip Rotating Handles, Max 400 lb - 2" Plate Adapters, Back & Chest Workout
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Cardio Training › Rowers
features: HEAVY DUTY BACK ROW MACHINE: It is constructed with 2"x 2" 12-gauge steel for strength and durability, and high-density dual-layered padding to last through your most intense back workout. Rubber end caps on each foot of the Row Machine provide additional stability to the frame and prevent damage to your home gym floor.

INDEPENDENT ARMS: Each arm on this seated row back pull machine works independently of each other. This gives you the option to work both sides of your back at the same time or in an alternating manner. Either way, this allows you to focus on each side of your back (without one side doing the bulk of the work), so you can strengthen each side of your back muscles including the lat muscles and spinal erectors, as well as your biceps as a secondary target

VERSATILE GRIPS: This workout machine includes a stationary grip handle that allows you to target your back muscles like a T Row T Bar Row Machine, as well as a rotating grip handle. The rotating grip handle allows you to pivot your arm naturally during the row for a more comfortable movement/workout with less strain on your elbows

ADJUSTABLE: The seat pad adjusts in 4 positions vertically to find the right height for you during your workout, while the chest pad adjusts in 5 different positions. The seat is tapered for a comfortable and natural position during your row workout.
PLATE LOADED- It can hold both standard and Olympic sized weights or bumper weight plates. Purchase includes 2 Olympic sleeve adapters, and both Olympic and standard sized spring clips
ADDITIONAL: The seated row and pull machine is perfect for athletes of all levels, in any home gym or light-commercial fitness center. Max weight load of 200 lb per arm - 400 lb total max weight load

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Plate Loaded Seated Rowing Back Machine – Premium Back Strengthening and Muscle Development for Home and Commercial Gyms 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Independent Arm Movements for Targeted Back and Bicep Development 
Break free from conventional rowing machines with our Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine featuring independent arms. This innovative design allows for simultaneous or alternating workouts, ensuring balanced back development and equal attention to both sides. Perfect for targeting lats, middle back, and biceps, this machine enhances your muscle development and strength training. Whether you’re training for endurance or building muscle, the independent arm movement provides a superior, personalized workout experience. Ideal for home gyms or commercial gym setups, this seated row machine is designed to improve back strength and overall upper body performance. Maximize your workout efficiency and achieve your fitness goals faster with this advanced feature. 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Rotating Hand Grips for Improved Back and Bicep Workouts 
In addition to the stationary grip handle that mimics the function of a T Row Machine, this Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine features a rotating grip handle for enhanced movement. This crucial design ensures natural arm movement during each row, minimizing elbow strain and promoting proper form. Ideal for muscle rehabilitation and physical therapy exercises, the rotating grip helps reduce stress on the joints while effectively targeting the lats, middle back, and biceps. Whether you're recovering from an injury or seeking to enhance overall strength, this feature ensures a comfortable and efficient workout experience. Perfect for users at any fitness level, this seated row machine is an excellent choice for both strength training and rehabilitation exercises. 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Rotating Hand Grips and Space-Saving Storage Design 
Versatility at its peak, the Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine is designed to accommodate both standard and Olympic-sized weights, allowing you to easily adjust the load for your workout. The package includes 2 Olympic sleeve adapters and clips for seamless switching between standard and Olympic plates. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 pounds, this machine is built to handle even the most intense workouts. Whether you're lifting heavy for strength training or performing lighter sets for muscle endurance, this row machine offers unmatched flexibility to meet your fitness needs. Perfect for home gyms or commercial setups, it’s a powerful tool for both muscle development and weight training. 
The seated rowing machine is an excellent choice for strengthening your back muscles, specifically the middle back and latissimus dorsi (lats), which are crucial for everyday movement and lifting. As an added benefit, biceps are engaged in the pulling motion, giving you a comprehensive workout that improves upper body strength. This plate loaded rowing machine is designed to help you achieve balanced muscle development in one effective machine, from the upper back to the arms. 
Built with heavy-duty steel, this rowing machine offers durability and longevity for both home and light-commercial gym use. It features thick steel construction with a 12-gauge steel frame to ensure it can handle heavy weight loads. The machine also includes rubber end caps, which prevent floor damage and provide stability during the most intense workouts. 
Unlike traditional rowing machines, this seated row machine features independent arms that allow for both simultaneous and alternating workouts. This unique design ensures that each side of your back receives equal attention, promoting balanced muscle development and helping to improve your posture and symmetry. 
This machine is equipped with multi-dimensional grip handles for a variety of training options. The stationary grip mimics the function of a traditional T Row Machine, while the rotating grip handle ensures a natural arm movement during each pull. By reducing strain on your elbows and improving your form, this feature makes your workouts more effective and comfortable. 
The Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine offers exceptional adjustability to accommodate users of all sizes and fitness levels. The 4-position adjustable seat pad and 5-position adjustable chest pad allow for a customized fit, while the tapered seat ensures maximum comfort throughout your rowing sessions. Whether you’re training for strength or endurance, you’ll be able to adjust the machine to your preferred position and achieve the best results. 
Designed for versatility, this rowing machine can hold both standard and Olympic-sized plates. With the included 2 Olympic sleeve adapters and weight clips, you can easily switch between weights, ensuring that your workouts are always challenging and progressive. Plate loaded systems allow for easy adjustments, making it ideal for those looking to push their limits in muscle development. 
This seated row machine is capable of supporting up to 200 lbs. per arm, for a total weight load of 400 lbs., making it perfect for even the most demanding lifting routines. Whether you're focusing on high-rep endurance sets or heavy lifting for muscle mass, this machine can handle it all. 
Designed with both home gym users and light-commercial gym settings in mind, the Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine is the perfect piece of equipment for anyone looking to strengthen and define their back muscles. With its sturdy design and versatile features, it’s an investment that will take your fitness to the next level. 
Durable Construction: Crafted from 12-gauge steel, this machine is built for long-term use, with a solid weight capacity of up to 400 lbs.
Independent Arms: Achieve even muscle development with independent arm movement for balanced back training.
Adjustable Comfort: Features a 4-position adjustable seat and 5-position chest pad for personalized workouts and optimal comfort.
Multi-Dimensional Grip: The rotating grip handle ensures proper form, minimizing elbow strain during rowing exercises.
Plate Loaded Design: Holds standard and Olympic-sized weights for added versatility and progression.
Versatile and Effective: Perfect for muscle development, including back, lats, biceps, and overall upper body strength.

title: GMWD Vertical Leg Press Machine, Leg Strength Training Machine with Linear Bearing, Lower Body Special Machine Home Gym
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: This vertical leg press machine is made of 50 x 100 mm, 14 gauge high quality steel. Gross weight: 94 lbs. Weight capacity: 550lbs. User height: higher than 5.3''.

Cost & Space Saving Choice: The GMWD vertical leg press machine is an excellent space saving machine. It's great for those who want to do leg press but don't have much space at home. Assemble size: 43.5’’ x 32.5’’ x 62’’. 50% less footprint than the normal 45°leg press machine. The full 1:1 ratio means that you don't need many weights, which is also a cost saving choice.

Ergonomic design: This leg machine has 3 positions backrest pad and head pad. Laying flat on the back pad, horizontally to the ground, your lower back, upper back, and neck, are almost completely left out of it. This can minimize lower back rounding and maintain your spine's natural curve. 5°Tilted and enlarged footboard is ergonomic and can be more comfortable while you are exercising.

Liner Bearing Design: Unlike other brands’ nylon bushings or roller bearings, we updated liner bearings. "Linear bearing" means a higher cost for GMWD but a better feeling for you. You won't feel any clogged while you're exercising. Start your leg training more coherently and smoothly.
3 start and end positions can meet the needs of people with different heights. Adjustable height range: 47.8'' to 62''. All your family members can enjoy the fun of leg strength training.
This leg press machine has 3 weight posts to help you add weights to your training. The detachable sleeves can fit both 1'' & 2'' plates.
Tilted and enlarged footboard is ergonomic and can be more comfortable while you are exercising. Leaflike texture for better slip resistance.

title: RitFit Leg Press Hack Squat Machine, Professional Adjustable Leg Press Machine for Home Gym with Linear Bearing, Specialty Hack Squat Machine for Full Lower Body Workout with Weight Storage Posts, Red
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: 【Stability & Versatile Workout】This two-in-one leg press and hack squat machine, red model, adopts linear bearings rather than rolling ones, and it is constructed of heavy-duty high tensile beefy steel. Beyond that, there are two weight plate storage holders at the rear bottom, when stacked up, greatly enhance machine's stability when in motion. By adjusting the placement of your feet on the foot plate, you can focus more on training isolating muscle groups.

【Multiple Adjustments】As a well-crafted design, there are 5 angle choices for hack squat and 3 for leg press setting, accomodating different sized athelets. The side rail (safety catches attached) handles can be pushed out to unlock the sled. After you are done with your set, pull both handles inward yourself to lock the sled in your designated lockout position. With a quick flip of the back pad and lowering of the leg press footplate, you can switch workouts in seconds to perform hack squat.

【Comfort & Smooth Exercise Experience】This leg press and hack squat gym machine features thick shoulder and backrest cushion wrapped in premium anti-slip and wear-resistant leather surface, providing ultimate and long-lasting comfort to ease your strain and stress, and protecting your bones and joints during your bodybuilding. Solid metal guide rods (sled) and aluminium alloy grips on both sides upgrade your workout experience without jerk motions.

【Safety & Considerate Design】The weight carriage fits 2'' plates, and Max 1200 lbs plate loading satisfies most users' needs. It is beginner-friendly, for experienced pro, you can do one leg at a time. Large diamond-plated footplate increases friction, preventing accidental sideslipping while in use. Two cushionings at the sled's bottom soften sudden impact with less noise. The triangular piece at the base of the back support also enhances overall stability.

【Separate Package】Our leg press and hack squat machine will be shipped in two separate packages to minimize the possibility of wear and tear due to collisions. Your packages may arrive on different dates. If you only receive part of the shipment, please be patient as we continuously monitor your logistics status. Backed by RitFit Lifetime Limited Warranty and friendly customer service, buy with confidence in RitFit!

description: Upgrade your home gym with this versatile Leverage Gym Machine that is designed to handle intense strength training sessions. Built for both durability and comfort, this gym machine ensures maximum flexibility for a variety of exercises. This Leverage Gym Machine combines strength, comfort, and versatility, making it an essential addition to any fitness enthusiast's home gym. features: SPECIFICATIONS: This leverage gym machine features assembled dimensions of 91.2 L x 60 W x 44.4 H inches, providing ample space for various exercises while maintaining a compact footprint suitable for most home gyms.

HEAVY-DUTY CONSTRUCTION: The machine is built with custom spec cold rolled steel tubing, capable of supporting significant weight loads. It meets ASTM standards, with tested capacities of 750 lbs for the bench and 375 lbs per arm. The recommended maximum weight is 600 lbs including user, with a bench capacity of 300 lbs and a leg developer capacity of 100 lbs. COMFORT & SUPPORT: Engineered for long-lasting comfort, the bench features a double-stitched boxed pad crafted from firm yet comfortable foam material, mounted on CARB-compliant plywood for strength and durability.

title: RitFit Leg Press Hack Squat Machine, Professional Adjustable Leg Press Machine for Home Gym with Linear Bearing, Specialty Hack Squat Machine for Full Lower Body Workout with Weight Storage Posts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Experience the stability and versatility of our leg press and hack squat machine. Angled at 45 degree, the entire structure ensures a safe and comfortable workout. Target various leg muscles utilizing the dual function of the inclined leg press and hack squat. The wider and thicker cushions are wrapped in high quality leather that is durable and easy to clean, allowing you to enjoy a more comfortable experience. Our machine prioritizes safety with solid guide rods, cushioning pads, and two storage for barbell plates. Adjustable footplate accomodate your body shape, providing an ergonomic exercise experience. Packed separately, we ensure minimal wear and tear during shipping. Expect packages to arrive on different dates, but rest assured as we will keep a close eye on the logistics for you.
features: 【Stability & Versatile Workout】This two-in-one leg press and hack squat machine is adapted linear bearings rather than rolling ones, and it is constructed of heavy-duty high tensile beefy steel. Beyond that, there are two weight plate storage holders at the rear bottom, when stacked up, greatly enhance machine's stability when in motion. By adjusting the placement of your feet on the foot plate, you can focus more on training isolating muscle groups.

【Comfort & Smooth Exercise Experience】This leg press and hack squat gym machine features thick shoulder and backrest cushion wrapped in premium anti-slip and wear-resistant leather surface, providing ultimate and long-lasting comfort to ease your strain and stress, and protecting your bones and joints during your bodybuilding. Solid metal guide rods (sled) and aluminium alloy grips on both sides upgrade your workout experience without jerk motions.

【Safety & Considerate Design】The weight carriage fits 2'' plates, and Max 1200 lbs plate loading satisfies most users' needs. It is beginner-friendly, for experienced pro, you can do one leg at a time. Large diamond-plated footplate increases friction, preventing accidental sideslipping while in use. Two cushionings at the sled's bottom soften sudden impact with less noise. The triangular piece at the base of the back support also enhances overall stability.

【Multiple Adjustments】As a well-crafted design, there are 5 angle choices for hack squat and 3 for leg press setting, accomodating different sized athelets. The side rail (safety catches attached) handles can be pushed out to unlock the sled. After you are done with your set, pull both handles inward yourself to lock the sled in your designated lockout position. With a quick flip of the back pad and lowering of the leg press footplate, you can switch workouts in seconds to perform hack squat.

【Separate Package】Our leg press and hack squat machine will be shipped in two separate packages to minimize the possibility of wear and tear due to collisions. Your packages may arrive on different dates. If you only receive part of the shipment, please be patient as we continuously monitor your logistics status. Backed by RitFit Lifetime Limited Warranty and friendly customer service, buy with confidence in RitFit!

title: Home Gym Multifunctional Exercise Equipment with 143 LBS Weight Stack,Pulley System, Fly Chest, and Leg Press Gym Equipment for Home Full Body Workout Machine
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Home Gym Systems
features: My name is Jennifer, and this is my first month using my cable machine home gym. As a busy professional, I've always wanted to be able to work out my whole body at home—not just by running or doing simple yoga routines. So, I began searching for gym equipment that could meet all my full-body training needs.

After careful comparison, I finally decided on this multi-functional fitness equipment, primarily because of its wide range of workout options and customizable adjustment features. First, it’s equipped with 13 weight pieces totaling 143 pounds, with adjustable weights that suit not only me but also my husband and family, meeting various fitness levels.

With this gym equipment, I do chest flys, leg training, pull-ups, low rows, chest presses, shoulder presses, leg extensions, and more. It allows me to comprehensively train my chest, back, legs, and even smaller muscles like abs and calves. It really covers everything, helping me achieve the results I want.

My family and I particularly appreciate the flexibility of this functional trainer. For instance, the butterfly arms can be adjusted to three levels, the leg press has adjustable height and forward-backward options, and the seat cushion can be set at four levels, providing a different support experience every time and making each workout comfortable and natural.

I also found that the L-shaped steel butterfly arm structure makes the setup very stable. The seat cushion is made from soft materials, so even during long workouts, it’s still comfortable. Most notably, the leg support and curl pad are detachable, so we can store them when not in use to save space. The pulley system of lat pulldown machines is specially designed to operate smoothly and quietly, so I don’t have to worry about disturbing my family.
A few days after buying it, I received the four packages shipped separately. With the detailed installation manual and tools, my husband and I only took a few hours to set it up—easy and convenient.

Now, I work out on this all in one gym every day, and I can already feel significant changes in my body. My husband also loves it; we take turns using it daily and enjoy sharing the fun of working out and the health benefits together. I’m so glad I chose this product. It not only provides a high-quality workout experience but also brings a positive, healthy activity into our home.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Marcy Standard Weight Bench with Butterfly and Leg Developer Home Gym MD-389 
The Marcy Standard Weight Bench with Butterfly and Leg Developer MD-389 gives an intense total body workout in the comfort of your own home. The set offers a 4-position back pad that you can easily adjust to various workout out positions to perform chest and other upper body exercises such as seated presses and curls. With the inclusion of proper padding and high density upholstery, the MD-389 provides the necessary comfort to keep you training as long as you need to. The standard weight bench is designed to last longer through rigorous workouts with its powder-coated heavy duty steel frame. This equipment is a great addition to your home gym if you want to achieve the perfect muscular body. This all-in-one set is an ideal choice for any level user looking to building, toning, and maintaining muscle mass. 
Butterfly Arms 
Unlike most other benches, the Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench MD-389 includes Butterfly Arms. Add weight plates to the post and you can do Butterfly Presses / Flys as you would at the gym. 
Preacher Curl Pad and Curl Handle 
The Marcy Diamond Elite Standard Weight Bench includes a Preacher Curl Pad and Curl Handle. To do Preacher Curls, simply add weight plates to the post below the Curl Handle and you’re set! 
Adjustable Back Pad 
Utilize the adjustable back pad to change up your workout. By inclining your back pad, you can target different parts of your muscles during Bench Presses or Flys. 
Preacher Curls 
Preacher Curls are similar to Curls. However, the Preacher Curl Pad helps you target your biceps while Curling – the Preacher Curl Pad prevents you from “cheating” during Curls.Dual-function leg developer for hamstrings, quadriceps, and glutes with four contoured foam roller pads to assist proper leg workouts. 
Leg Extensions

features: HEAVY DUTY- Constructed with 2” x 2” steel frame with high-density, dual-layered pad measuring 44” x 9. 5” x 2”. U-shaped base ensures strength and durability throughout frame while ankle pads provide safety to user during ab crunch function.

aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Chest Press Machine with Independent Converging Arms for a Unique Workout 
Adjustable Flat or Incline Chest Bench Press with Ab Crunch Feature 
The extra long seat pad allows the user to adjust their position for a different range of motion or to target the muscles from a different angle. The high-density, dual-layered pad folds down for the incline bench feature and acts as an ab crunch board. The foam ankle pads secure the user and support ankles and knees when performing ab crunches. The safety catches allow each arm to be rested when not in use and protect the user in the event the lift cannot be completed. Each safety catch, featuring a protective rubber strip, has 9 different adjustment positions using a locking pin, allowing an 8” range. A plate storage peg is featured on both sides of the unit to allow a clean and organized home gym. 
Each weight & storage peg measures 8” long and 1” in diameter. To convert plate storage pegs to 2" for Olympic style plates, the EX-10 adaptor is sold separately. 
This weight bench station has a Maximum Weight load of 125 lbs per arm, allowing users to train with up to 250 lbs. total. 
Maximize Your Home Gym Workout - Upper Body & Core Routines 
Flat Bench- Chest Press 
Flat bench presses are best for overall development of the pectoralis, commonly known as the pecs or your chest muscles. With this natural and fluid movement, it is likely to assist you in daily life activities as well as other exercises! 
Incline Bench - Chest Press 
With a similar movement to the flat bench, performing incline bench presses will activate your shoulders as well as the upper part of the pecs. The incline press puts less strain on your rotator cuff while activating the deltoids. 
Ab Crunch Feature 
Using the high density pad supports by the head of the bench, you can secure yourself by placing your feet behind them and perform ab crunches while the bench is in the incline position, allowing you to add more variation to your workout!

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Uses patented, "Arc Movement" for full range of motion to rapidly develop a bigger, stronger, leaner chest. 
Customized resistance levels suits beginners to expert bodybuilders. 
Fully assembled machine is portable and easy to store. 
How does it work? 
Iron Chest Master is designed to keep joints protected while maximizing growth of chest, shoulders, triceps, upper back and abs. All the way through the movement from push-up through the peak contraction, your body is stable with no damaging rotation of the wrists or shoulder joints. 
Are the resistance bands adjustable or universal? 
The resistance bands of the Iron Chest Master are adjustable -- resistance ranging from 60 lbs to 120+ lbs. Resistance bands can be individually substituted in order to customize the resistance level of the machine to suit the individual user. 
What are the dimensions and weight? 
Iron Chest Master is 48" x 6" x 4" and the weight is 7 lbs. 
How much weight can it hold? 
The bearings on the machine can hold up to 300 lbs. per handle, so a total of 600 lbs. of pressure. It would be almost impossible to place that type of stress on the machine.

Product Description
Previous page
8 Backrest Positions

5 Heights Adjustable

GREAT ADJUSTABILITY 
1 8-postion backrest 2 5-height rack 3 5-height pad 
FULL-BODY WORKOUT 
BENCH PRESS 
The bench press targets chest, triceps, and shoulders. It builds strength as well as encouraging the growth of these muscle groups. FLYBIRD Weight Bench features its great adjustability of 8 backrest positions. You can choose an appropriate positions to better meet your fitness levels and goals. 
PREACHER CURL 
Preacher curl brings multiple benefits that you might not find in conventional bicep curl. It is necessary to keep a good form and avoid cheating while performing arm workouts. Using the pad can force you into negative movement, which improves strength and muscles growth. 
LEG EXTENSION 
The leg extension is an excellent movement for strengthening your quadriceps, the large muscles of the front of the thigh. Different from squat, this is an“open-chain kinetic”exercise. Building your quads can increase the force of kicking movements, which can be beneficial in sports performance. 
LYING LEG CURL 
Leg curls target hamstrings and calf muscles. The leg developer moves smoothly and you can get a full range of motion. When lowering feet back down, your buttocks, quadriceps, and front of the shins are activated too. Strong hamstrings are essential for overall strength, balance, and stamina. 
COMFORTABLE PADDING 
High-density foam padding with a stronger double-stitched seam supports your body and reduces muscle fatigue. 
CONTOURED FOAM ROLLER 
The soft foam roller pads stay on well to support your knees and ankles while performing sit-ups or other leg exercises. 
DUAL-FUNCTION LEG DEVELOPER 
220 lbs max weight capacity. There is a plastic buffer to keep metal from grinding at the joint. The locking mechanism allows you to do ab exercises. 
WEIGHT STORAGE POST 
You can place plates on the 1-inch weight storage posts to increase stability and avoid cluttering your workout space. 3 spring clip collars included.

Tubular Cross Bar
Different from circular steel tube, the tubular cross bar fits in well with the backrest, which offers support when you doing bench press.

Extended Leg Bases
21-inch flat rear leg bases and triangular structure ensure the outstanding stability of the bench to withstand heavy weight lifting.

Adjustable Square Foot Caps
We utilize FLYBIRD exclusive adjustable foot caps, which can be rotated to accommodate uneven floors for stability.

title: Smith Machine, 2000LBS Power Rack with Smith Bar, Cable Crossover Machine and Chest Station Machine for Home Gym, Multifunctional Home Gym System with LAT Pulldown System and More Attachment
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Racks & Cages › Smith Machines
features: [ALL IN ONE]: This Smith Machine is designed to target different muscle groups, combines many functions such as Smith machine, squat rack, cable crossover machine, butterfly chest press, pull-up station, etc., You can perform exercises such as barbell bench press, butterfly chest fly, rowing, lat pulldown, squats, straight-leg deadlifts, bicep curls, tricep pushdowns, and hanging leg raises, ensuring a smooth workout experience for fitness enthusiasts of all levels.

[High-Strength Durability]: Dual Smith bars made of solid steel with hard chrome plating ensure long-lasting wear resistance. The linear bearing sliding sleeves on the barbell provide smooth operation during exercises, preventing jamming and enhancing workout comfort.

[Upgraded Cable System]: Use commercial-grade 7-strand cables, stronger than the 5-strand cables used in most products, and wrapped in PU on the outside, which has stronger wear resistance than ordinary PVC. Upgraded to PU pulleys, which have higher strength and toughness and will not break even under high-intensity impacts.

[Enhanced Safety Features]: Adjustable safety limiters on the Smith bars with 15 positioning slots on the frame allow you to set the optimal safety position for different exercises and body types, ensuring comprehensive protection and peace of mind during every workout. The outer safety arm provides added protection for a broader range of training movements and can be transformed into a stool with the included seat cushion.

[Durability and Strength]: Constructed from 2"x2" 1.6mm thick robust steel. This multifunctional home gym machine total weight capacity of 2000 lbs, and offers exceptional durability and stability, making it a reliable choice for both novice and experienced fitness enthusiasts.

[NOTICE]: Our Smith machine home gym will be shipped in three packages (May not arrive at the same time) to reduce wear and tear due to collisions. If you encounter any problems during the installation process, please contact us and our professional service team will answer you promptly. Weight plates NOT included.

What are the upgardes of the cable system? 
It has reached light commercial grade quality, uses 7-strand cable with stronger load capacity than ordinary 5-strand cable, and is wrapped with PU material, which has stronger wear resistance and tensile resistance than traditional PVC. 
What are the advantages of PU pulleys? 
The pulley is upgraded from nylon to PU material, which can withstand higher intensity impact, solving the problem of nylon pulleys being easy to break under high load conditions.
